Busia county chief Education officer Joel Barua has faulted MCAs for criticising the governor&rsquo;s development record.On Tuesday, he said claims by Bunyala South MCA Stephen Omenda and Alice Chevi that the ward was denied bursary allocations are a &ldquo;figment of their imagination&rdquo;.&ldquo; Leaders should sober up and play politics on facts,&rdquo; Barua said.